  "body": "## Proposal to change besu from \r\n  id 'com.github.hierynomus.license' version '0.16.1-fix'\r\nto\r\n  id 'com.github.jk1.dependency-license-report' version '2.0'\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n* No regression on the Gradle checkLicenses task - build will still fail if dependencies use unapproved licenses\r\n* downloadLicenses task takes no more than 1 minute\r\n\r\n## Background\r\nThis is now used by other consensys open source projects including: Teku, EthSigner, Web3Signer, Signers. \r\nhttps://github.com/jk1/Gradle-License-Report\r\n\r\nexample config:\r\nthis file matches the format besu already uses:\r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/master/gradle/check-licenses.gradle\r\nthis one may be new:\r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/master/gradle/license-report-config/allowed-licenses.json\r\n",
